vice presidential
debate.

00:25.659 --> 00:30.898 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
GWEN IFILL: And from the
classroom to the
campaign trail -- why Oklahoma
teachers are

00:30.931 --> 00:35.569 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
