turn the state's
failing education system around.

00:35.602 --> 00:37.671 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ANGELA CLARK LITTLE, Oklahomans
for Public
Education: A lot of legislators
feel like

00:37.704 --> 00:40.340 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
