attempt.

08:06.419 --> 08:11.491 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Russia airstrikes
blasted Eastern
Aleppo in Syria again today.

08:11.524 --> 08:15.895 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
