08:26.873 --> 08:30.310 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN KERRY, U.S. Secretary of
State: We will
continue, as we have before, to
pursue a meaningful,

08:30.343 --> 08:36.516 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
