08:53.133 --> 08:58.471 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: And Moscow announced
it has deployed
an advanced surface-to-air
missile system

08:58.505 --> 09:00.306 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
in Syria for the first time.

09:00.340 --> 09:05.745 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: A U.S. military
service person
was killed by a roadside bomb in
Afghanistan

09:05.779 --> 09:07.280 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
today.

09:07.313 --> 09:10.717 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
