Taliban gunmen
held the city for three days.

09:26.166 --> 09:31.137 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: In economic news,
new worries
about Britain's exit from the
European Union

09:31.171 --> 09:32.739 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
weighed on Wall Street.

09:32.772 --> 09:38.545 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
