slipped 10.

09:41.981 --> 09:47.287 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And three
British-born scientists
who teach in the U.S. have won
this year's

09:47.320 --> 09:49.489 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
