third, backhanded
by Blake.

47:35.119 --> 47:37.354 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
He straightens up to throw him
out.

47:37.388 --> 47:39.290 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Easy inning for Randy Wolf.

47:39.323 --> 47:44.361 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: In Los Angeles,
but also, incredibly,
going all the way back to
Brooklyn in the

47:44.395 --> 47:45.629 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
1950s.

47:45.663 --> 47:48.599 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
VIN SCULLY: The pitch at the
