47:48.632 --> 47:50.367 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Ball one.

47:50.401 --> 47:55.673 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Now, admittedly, there are days
where you
think, you know, I'd rather sit
under a tree

47:55.706 --> 47:57.108 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
