47:57.141 --> 47:58.109 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: Yes.

47:58.142 --> 47:59.777 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Everybody has those days, right?

47:59.810 --> 48:03.147 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
VIN SCULLY: But what's great is,
you come
to the park, you do the routine
stuff, and

48:03.180 --> 48:08.719 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
