the field, and the crowd roars.

48:08.753 --> 48:13.124 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And, all of a sudden, you're
delighted as
a kid in a candy store.

48:13.157 --> 48:14.859 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: That's exactly
where you want
to be.

48:14.892 --> 48:16.927 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
VIN SCULLY: Exactly.

48:16.961 --> 48:20.164 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: In an age when
