48:25.236 --> 48:30.641 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: His style,
mastery of language,
and, yes, longevity have made
him a legend

48:30.674 --> 48:32.643 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
in sports circles.

48:32.676 --> 48:38.649 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It all began, he says, with
lessons in attitude
from his mentor, Red Barber,
another broadcasting

48:38.682 --> 48:43.120 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
great, who gave Scully his first
