and brought him into the booth
in Brooklyn

48:43.154 --> 48:44.855 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
in 1950.

48:44.889 --> 48:49.627 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
VIN SCULLY: One of my many jobs
as the junior
partner of the broadcasting firm
would be

48:49.660 --> 48:52.062 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
