crawl under
the radio.

51:26.550 --> 51:29.720 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I would listen to a game
that meant nothing
to a kid growing up in New York.

51:29.753 --> 51:32.423 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I mean, it might be
Tennessee-Alabama.

51:32.456 --> 51:38.595 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But when someone scored a
touchdown and the
crowd roared, that crowd noise
would come

51:38.629 --> 51:44.301 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
