out of a showerhead,
and it would just cover me with
goose bumps.

51:44.335 --> 51:48.439 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I used to think, oh, I would
like to be
there to feel that roar of the
crowd.

51:48.472 --> 51:54.211 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
