51:55.813 --> 51:57.281 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: But you're still
enjoying what
you're doing?

51:57.314 --> 51:58.515 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
VIN SCULLY: I love it.

51:58.549 --> 52:00.317 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And you know how I know I love
it?

52:00.351 --> 52:05.889 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Because, when there's a great
play on the
field and the crowd roars, I
still get goose

52:05.923 --> 52:06.890 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
bumps.

52:06.924 --> 52:09.159 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
